{"tid":988234,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/Steam] 香港Arma 3軍事模擬團隊招募","createTime":"2019-01-20T01:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T00:11:55.000Z","uid":164307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c814396c7feb0654f7df7e8c4c391795146aa17","tid":988234,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:29:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbZDP3P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbZDP3P.jpg&h=0722d867&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</div><br />\n小弟間中見到連登有人問有冇人打Arma 3，但好多都失落而回。呢隻game都出咗成五年有多都仲係得好少數香港人肯玩，其實佢入面有好多潛在吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n數數遊戲模式都成十幾種，除咗官方既Campaign，PVP之外，亦有為人所熟識既Exile(Arma 3 DayZ)，King of The Hill，Altis Life，Wasteland等等數之不盡既模式。所以小弟先更加想組織一班打Arma 3既香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">簡介</span></ins></strong><br />\nBrotherhood of Wolf [BOWHK]，狼群，係一隊廣東話既Arma3軍事模擬隊伍。團隊作風係以輕鬆半擬真既態度打機。背景以德國聯邦國防軍為藍本，我哋有時都會打下唔同國家唔同時期。<br />\n<br />\n我哋自己擁有獨立既伺服器，每逢星期六日準時九點鐘開波打自製既Arma3 Coop Mission。得閒星期一至五亦會去人哋公開ser搞搞震，例如King of The Hill，Invade &amp; Annex，Warlord之類。除咗Arma3之外呢度亦係一個遊戲吹水台，一個各路英雄雲集既地方。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">廢話</span></ins></strong><br />\n團隊既中心只憑兩隻字  - 《尊重》我哋打機為求既無非都係為咗開心，所以對團隊嚟講軍階職位都只不過係泡沬，基本尊重先至係最重要。真心話用外語講會真心啲((好似係))，所以隊徽入面用咗句德文既名言， &lsquo;&lsquo;Wer nicht vorw&auml;rts geht, der kommt zur&uuml;cke&rsquo;&rsquo; ，中文解釋為「不進則退」。當中所意味既並非個人既進步，而係希望成Team人一齊既努力奮鬥 ，搏盡無悔。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">收生要求</span></ins></strong><br />\n我哋收生要求非常簡單，只要你擁有Arma3 加上你願意同其他人合作即可。不論你係肥矮毒柒，如果你有心我哋就一定會收留你。歡迎任何人用下面兩種方式查詢或聯絡我哋。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/BOWHK2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FBOWHK2018&d=ugoaPMJGAUOlqu0hTQrapNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d69d1df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/BOWHK2018</a><br />\nDiscord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BAPZxXW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FBAPZxXW&d=ugoaPMJGAUOlqu0hTQrapNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d37528fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/BAPZxXW</a>"},{"pid":"093f4917841fef8412164e6ffc5a6217cb6ce126","tid":988234,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">圖定老母</span></ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smSRqT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsmSRqT4.jpg&h=d6ead724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hkhaGsq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhkhaGsq.jpg&h=69b661f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q6DX5T6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6DX5T6.jpg&h=969c670b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8d1N7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8d1N7s.jpg&h=1c2f01cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mrCmsU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mrCmsU.jpg&h=a5500d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">Link定老母</span></ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XPh_tszhbnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXPh_tszhbnY&d=ugoaPMJGAUOlqu0hTQrapNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=aca9038e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XPh_tszhbnY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W3GHr4C01_Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be